                    <span class="detailsEffetSort"> &nbsp:&nbsp </span><span class="detailsEffetSort">2 mana + niveau</span></p>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="divInterneClasse">
        <div class="divSortTechnique divSortTechniqueSansOmbre">
